nodes.text: This untitled propaganda poster was created by the Galactic Empire. It depicted the Imperial enforcer Darth Vader charging with his lightsaber activated. The background was filled with various soldiers, including two stormtroopers, a Royal Guard, a scout trooper, a snowtrooper, an Imperial Army trooper, an TIE pilot, and an Imperial Navy trooper; to Vader's right, a message was written in High Galactic which read "He can't do it alone!" The last word was highlighted in red, and at the bottom, another message, between two Imperial crest logos, declared "Enlist Today!"
This image was created by Cliff Chiang. It was originally made for 2010 Topps Star Wars Galaxy Series 5, a 2010 series of Legends trading cards by Topps.
